OL,3,C'That ship saved our lives': John
OL,4,CHeys' SS Vega memories 80 years on
OL,6,FJohn Heys' story:
OL,8,FJohn was born in 1937. His early
OL,9,Fchildhood lived in the shadow of the
OL,10,FGerman Occupation.
OL,12,FHe recalls: "I had no concerns or
OL,13,Fworries at all. I knew nothing else.
OL,15,F"If you're born into something it's
OL,16,Fquite natural, so for me the Germans
OL,17,Fwere friendly - they were friendly
OL,18,Fpeople.
