OL,3,C'That ship saved our lives': John
OL,4,CHeys' SS Vega memories 80 years on
OL,6,FAnother memory John vividly remembers
OL,7,Fis the Christmas of 1943: the day his
OL,8,Fblack labrador, Jack, caught a rabbit
OL,9,Fand brought it home to the family.
OL,11,FJohn says: "I opened the door and he
OL,12,Fwas sitting there with a big rabbit in
OL,13,Fhis mouth.
OL,15,F"He'd been down on Ouaisne Common and
OL,16,Fcaught one but he hadn't eaten it - he
OL,17,Fbrought it back and we all had a bit
OL,18,Fof rabbit for Christmas."
