OL,3,C'That ship saved our lives': John
OL,4,CHeys' SS Vega memories 80 years on
OL,6,FAfter the D-day landings in Normandy,
OL,7,Fthe tide of war began to turn and by
OL,8,Fthe winter of 1944, hope arrived in
OL,9,FJersey.
OL,11,FJohn Heys was 7 years old when the SS
OL,12,FVega ship came to the island, carrying
OL,13,Fprecious cargo.
OL,15,FHe recalls: "That ship saved our
OL,16,Flives, the day we got our Red Cross
OL,17,Fparcels.
