OL,3,C'That ship saved our lives': John
OL,4,CHeys' SS Vega memories 80 years on
OL,6,FJohn adds: "My sister and I grabbed
OL,7,Fthe tin of KLIM and we ran upstairs
OL,8,Fand dived under the bed and we had a
OL,9,Flittle screwdriver we used to prise
OL,10,Fthe top off.
OL,12,F"We grabbed this powder and put it in
OL,13,Four mouths but we couldn't swallow it
OL,14,Fbecause we didn't have enough saliva
OL,15,Fto break it down and we were stuck."
