OL,3,C'That ship saved our lives': John
OL,4,CHeys' SS Vega memories 80 years on
OL,6,FIt wasn't just the food products that
OL,7,Fwere new to John: for the first time,
OL,8,Fhe had toiletries after years of going
OL,9,Fwithout.
OL,11,FJohn explains: "I remember my mother
OL,12,Fshowing me how to clean my teeth: you
OL,13,Fgot a toothbrush and you rubbed it
OL,14,Finside the fireplace on the soot to
OL,15,Fclean your teeth.
OL,17,F"To have toothpaste was unbelievable -
OL,18,Fwe wanted to eat it let alone clean
OL,19,Four teeth."
