OL,4,CHeys' SS Vega memories 80 years on
OL,6,FAs time passes, John reflects on the
OL,7,Fexperience of the Occupation, stating:
OL,8,F"These events gradually disappear and
OL,9,Flose their importance, but those of us
OL,10,Fwho were here at the time will never
OL,11,Fever forget what went on."
